insert  into `oc_category_description`(`category_id`,`language_id`,`name`,`description`,`meta_title`,`meta_description`,`meta_keyword`,`footer_keywords`) values (60,1,'Rigid Signs',' &lt;h2&gt;Rigid Signs&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n          &lt;img alt=&quot;Rigid Signs&quot; src=&quot;image/catalog/pro-list.png&quot;&gt;\r\n          &lt;p&gt;Banners Expo is a New York City based sign company that serves the entire US, offering affordable signage with quality design. We work with thousands of local companies (and individuals) and hundreds more spread out across the United States, including Los Angeles, California. Boston, Massachusetts, and even Houston, Texas.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We are best known for our banners. But we got our start with all types of sign design and fabrication, and we have a huge manufacturing facility capable of designing quality signs of all shapes and sizes. Our “rigid signs” – signs that are designed to be flat with a rigid material – are some of our most common. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;What Are Rigid Signs?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;As the name implies, rigid signs are any type of sign that is designed to be flat, strong, and capable of withstanding weather. Many rigid signs are primarily indoor signs, although some, like aluminum signs, make excellent and resilient outdoor signs as well.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Banners Expo has over 30 years of experience with sign fabrication. This allows us to not only create rigid signs more efficiently (thus lowering the cost for you). It also means that we can help recommend specific types of signs depending on what you need. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Some examples of our rigid signs include:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Foam Board Signs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;PVC Signs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Aluminum Signs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Gator Board Signs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Coroplast Signs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We frequently make rigid plastic signs, such as plastic lawn signs, as well as political campaign signs, real estate signage, and so much more. We have made signs for almost every industry imaginable, including restaurants, manufacturing plants, accountants, tech companies – business both large and small, as well as individuals that need signs for personal reasons.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Custom rigid signs are also a specialty of ours. We have numerous customization options to help make sure that any message you’re trying to get out there is able to be viewed exactly as you envisioned. Some of these customization options include:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Engraved Plastic&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Illumination&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Wood Posts&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Of course, you can also customize the colors of the printing, the colors of the sign backgrounds (especially for plastic, coroplast, and foam board), and so much more. We have numerous size options as well, with the ability to create signs as small as a postage stamp or as large as a billboard – possibly even larger.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Rigid signs can be one or two sided. They can be used both indoors and outdoors (depending on the material). We make it possible to create nearly any sign that you need, and we will do whatever it takes to make sure that you’re satisfied with your purchase.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Order Rigid Signs from Banners Expo&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We are based in New York City, serving Brooklyn, Manhattan, Staten Island, the Bronx, and Queens. But we also have clients across the United States – from nearby New Jersey and Pennsylvania, to distant areas like Raleigh, NC, San Diego, CA, Seattle, WA, and more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We accept designs in EPS, .AI, .PSD, .JPG, .PNG &amp;amp; .PDF file formats. But for those that do not yet have a design, we also have some of the most affordable and skilled sign designers that can turn your ideas and needs into a full color sign in any size or style. Our graphic designers are sign specialists, able to turn any idea you have into a real, tangible sign that maximizes viewership. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our team specializes in quality craftsmanship and customer service, and each and every person that works for our team makes it their goal to help you feel like our one and only customer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Contact Banners Expo Today to Get Started&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Banners Expo is proud to be the leading choice for rigid sign fabrication, banners, and so much more. With over 30 years of experience and a team of truly talented signage staff, we genuinely believe in what we do, and we believe that we can help all of our clients achieve their advertising, marketing, branding, or other sign related goals. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in learning more about any of our rigid signs, or you would like to find out more about our costs and services, please do not hesitate to give us a call today at 1-718-252-7575. We’re happy to talk to you about any questions you may have, or give you more information about material choices and other design related options. &lt;/p&gt;','Rigid Signs NYC | Gator Board Signs Corrugated Plastic Signs','','','Rigid Signs nyc,Rigid Plastic signs,Rigid Sign printing,Rigid Aluminum signs,Rigid Custom Aluminum signage,Rigid Foam board Signs,Rigid Gator Board Signs,Rigid Coroplast Signs'),(62,1,'Floor Stands','&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Floor Stands&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Displays&quot; src=&quot;image/catalog/pro-list.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;At their core, signs are about spreading a message. From billboards to vehicle signs to outdoor signs and more, all of them are specifically designed to be seen. The only difference is how they target those people and where the signs are located.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Some of the best signs are those that are placed directly in front of everyone walking by. These signs, known as display stands or display signs, do a great job of capturing the eye of pedestrians. They are used at trade shows and placed on walkways inside and outside in order to share information, such as:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Advertisements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Restaurant Menus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Specials/Clearance Sales, and More&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;There is really no limit to the number of ways to use display stands, and at Banners Expo, we provide some of the most affordable and attractive display stands available today, and provide these display signs and retail floor stands to businesses in New York City and across the United States.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Our Floor Stands Services at Banners Expo&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;These types of promotional banner displays are simply one of the most effective ways to spread a message, and at Banners Expo, we proudly create these banner stands for companies across the US. We are based in NYC, and service areas like Brooklyn, Manhattan, Staten Island, Queens, and the Bronx. But we also have affordable rates and expert service that makes us a great choice for New Jersey, Texas, California, Ohio, Florida, and everywhere in between.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are able to offer a variety of custom display stand sizes, each one with its own unique features, low costs, and benefits. We have floor display stands for both indoor and outdoor use, and these stands are available in multiple sizes and colors so that you can use them for any purpose.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Why Use Banners Expo?&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;With wholesale pricing that is ideal for those in any state across the country, Banners Expo is the best choice for all of your display stands. We do our best to create stunning custom signs that are exactly what your business is looking for, and are happy to 