insert  into `oc_product_description`(`product_id`,`language_id`,`name`,`description`,`tag`,`meta_title`,`meta_description`,`meta_keyword`,`footer_keywords`) values (51,1,'Mesh Banners','&lt;p&gt;Banners are the best way to advertise a product or service. But not all banners are created equal. Depending on the look you’re trying to achieve or the area you’re planning to advertise, these signs need a specific type of material in order to maximize their outreach and engage the right amount of viewers. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Mash banners are perhaps one of the most popular. Mesh banners are a type of banner option that is created with a slightly see through mesh material. This material allows a very small amount of the background to peak through, without affecting the look and feel of the banner’s content. For those that are interested in purchasing a custom mesh banner, there is no better place than Banners Expo.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Order a Custom Mesh Banner at Banners Expo&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The idea behind mesh banners is that allowing the light and color of the background to shine through the sign gives the banner a more easily visible and natural appearance. The mesh material also allows wind to easily pass through the sign so that it is a better fit for outdoor use. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;While traditional vinyl banners have a tendency to whip around in the wind, possibly distracting viewers form the look at of the banner, mesh banners are stable. They are able to maintain their place on walls, fences, and more, and are all capable of making sure that you are always on message.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Why Order a Mesh Banner from Banners Expo?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Banners Expo is the leader in banner stand fabrication and development across the continental United States. Based in New York City, we serve everywhere from Maine to California, Florida to Washington, Michigan to Texas – anywhere that a company needs an affordable, well crafted banner.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our banners are crafted to match your needs perfectly, with a variety of design elements and options to choose from in order to ensure that you have the perfect banner stand for you:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Seam Mesh Printing vs. Seamless Mesh Printing – We offer both seamless and with seam mesh banner printing options, allowing you a choice in how you want your design to look.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Hemming Options – For those that are looking for hemming with their mesh banner as a finishing option, we are happy to hem any of our mesh banner prints.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Outdoor Specifications – For outdoor mesh banner printing, we have many additional options including water proof and UV safe options that will help the mesh banner last a lifetime. &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Reinforcement – We have many finishing options available, including reinforced webbing and reinforced hemming – both of which can help your mesh banner look its best.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Color Grommets – We have several color grommets available with our mesh banners, including white grommets, black grommets, and silver grommets.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our team can work with nearly any design you send over. But if you don’t have a design, we also have our own team of trained single side mesh banner designers that are able to turn your vision into a reality, with customization options and beautiful designs that will help your sign stand out. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Contact Banners Expo Today for Custom Mesh Banner Printing&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;When it comes to mesh banners, there is no company that offers the same reliability and service that we offer at Banners Expo. From large billboard mesh banners to smaller signs placed in and around properties, we offer the best combination of banner printing and sign services for those that are looking to create an amazing indoor or outdoor sign using custom mesh material.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our Brooklyn based company serves more than simply the five boroughs of New York (Brooklyn, Manhattan, the Bronx, Queens, and Staten Island). We also service the needs of companies and individuals across the United States, with many fast turnaround options available and the ability to match nearly any of your sign’s specifications. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;If you are in need of a custom mesh banner, or would like to talk more about the benefits of all different types of banner material, please contact us today at 1-718-252-7575. Our team is ready and able to help you find the perfect banner for your needs, or design one according to your vision and the ideas that you are looking to promote. Please call us today to get started, and see why we are the leader in banner and sign development. &lt;/p&gt;','','Custom Mesh Banners Online, Outdoor Full Color Mesh Advertising Banners for Sale','','','Mesh Banner, Custom Mesh Banner, Outdoor Mesh Banner Printing, Single Side Mesh Vinyl Banner, Vinyl Mesh Printing, Billboard Mesh Banners, Mesh Vinyl Banners, Mesh Banner Signs, Mesh Banner Fast turn around'),(59,1,'Paper Posters','&lt;p&gt;\r\n    When it comes to affordable signage, the paper poster sign is still, even today, one of the most popular types of signs available. Paper posters remain a top choice for businesses, event planners, and more that are trying to get their name and their brand out there. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    At Banners Expo, our NYC based paper poster company can print posters of all sizes, with numerous colors and options that make us a great choice both in New York and abroad.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Our Paper Poster Printing Services&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Custom poster printing is our specialty. While many of our clients are in NY and the 5 boroughs, we also service New Jersey, Pennsylvania, and as far away as Los Angeles and Seattle. We create a host of different types of posters including, but not at all limited to:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Restaurant Posters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Sports Event Posters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Music Concert or Album Release Posters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Movie Posters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Marketing and Advertising Posters&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We can even create large, full color posters for academic papers, create noticeable posters for trade shows – whatever type of paper poster you need, our team can make sure that it is expertly crafted based on your specifications.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Our Customization Options for Paper Poster Printing&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    At Banners Expo, we make every effort to ensure that your posters have every quality you need to spread a message and get attention. We offer a variety of customization options that make us the right choice for your paper printing needs. Just a small sample of these custom poster services includes:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Types – We have two different types of paper posters available. We have poster paper and photo paper. Both are an excellent option for those that need to print in large scale color.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Sizes – We can print in a variety of sizes, from small to very, very large. We’re a full service sign company, which means that we are capable of creating signs in the size and style you want and need.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Indoor and Outdoor – Posters are notoriously fragile, but if you are planning to create a sign that is ready for outdoor use, we can still use the material and printing process that allows it to withstand some degree of weather.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    From event publicity posters to large poster printing, there is almost no type of poster we cannot create for those that need it, along with customer service that will ensure your satisfaction.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Nearly Any Type of File Accepted – Design Elements Available&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We accept a variety of file types with your designs, including EPS, .AI, .PSD, .JPG, .PNG and PDF. It is best if image size is the same as the print size. What makes Banners Expo the bests choice for your poster printing is that we also provide design options. We can create an advertising or marketing sign that spreads your message and is designed to your specifications. If you do not have a graphic designer in house, let the team at Banners Expo help make sure that your poster is ready for printing.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Contact Banners Expo Today&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    At Banners Expo, our belief is providing those around New York City and across the country with the high quality custom posters – and other signs – that they need to continue to market their company or share their message. We are happy and able to help you with the process, from design to choosing the materials, or we can make it our priority to ensure that you have all of your posters as quickly as possible.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    If you are interested in learning more about our poster printing services, contact Banners Expo today. We are based in New York City, serving areas like Brooklyn, Manhattan, Staten Island, and more, and we also create signs for cities like Seattle, San Francisco, Austin, Portland, and so much more. With the ability to ship anywhere in United States, we are confident that our poster printing services are the right choice for you. Please call us today at 1-718-252-7575  to get started.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','Paper Signs | Large Format Paper Poster Printing Company','','','Paper Poster Printing,Custom poster printing,Large Online poster printing,Events publicity posters,Sports events posters,Restaurant posters'),(57,1,'Window wraps','&lt;p&gt;\r\n    While many businesses look at windows as a way to bring in light, savvy companies know that outward facing windows can also be a great way to advertise your business or services. The windows of your property represent unused real estate, and when used correctly they can provide you with a type of advertising and branding that few other signs can provide. When you need custom window wraps, contact Banners Expo today. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;What Are Window Wraps?&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Window wraps are a type of thin vinyl sign that fits directly over your windows. Some window wraps cover the entirety of the window. Others are more like window graphics, covering a part of the window but leaving the rest open for added light and visibility.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    But no matter the type of wrap, the idea is to make sure that windows are more than just a window. They are a way to provide your company with branding and advertising on space that you already own. More and more companies have started to use full color window signage in order to give their business far more visual impact because few other types of on-site signs are as large and noticeable as window signs.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;\r\n    Window Wrap Customization Options\r\n&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Banners Expo is based in Brooklyn. We have hundreds of clients across NYC, spreading from Manhattan to the Bronx to Staten Island to Queens. From NYC, we can also travel as far as most of New Jersey and Philadelphia and provide installation services when necessary.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    But beyond NYC, we also serve areas like Atlanta, Miami, San Jose, Seattle, Phoenix, Los Angeles – if you are in need of high quality, custom window graphics and wraps, Banners Expo is the number one choice anywhere in the United States. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Our window sign services are designed to match any type of need or vision you may have. That is why we are able to offer customization services, including:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Finishing – We can customize the finishing of your sign, giving it options like matte design and gloss design depending on the luster you were looking for.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Cut – We have many different cut options available as well. We can do a traditional rectangular or straight cut that goes over the entirety of your window, or we can do a die cut option that is shaped in the style that is best for your vision.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Size – Custom window wrap and graphic sizes are our specialty. We can create graphics both small and larger, and no matter the size we can make sure that it is the style, shape, and colors that you wanted.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    \r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We also have fast shipping options available, and our installation services for the local area are very affordable. Our window wraps are also designed to be easy to install, so no matter where you are located you’ll be able to have the custom sign you need perfectly placed on your window.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Our Commitment to Superior Service&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Banners Expo believes in creating quality signs with excellent customer service. There is no better company to deliver the best in window graphics for your business, because we are more than just a typical sign company. If you have any questions or you’re not sure what signs are best for you, we are happy to answer your questions and assist you in their creation.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We also have trained sign designers on staff, so that if you find that you don’t have the manpower to design these types of graphics, our team of sign creators can make the signs for you and ensure that you are ready to start advertising your business today. With full color and in-depth designs available, you’ll love your custom window decals and signage.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Contact Banners Expo Today&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Banners Expo has some of the most affordable prices available today, and we have more than 30 years of experience creating signs so that you can be sure that you’re getting a team with immense expertise to handle your window signage needs. For more information about our sign services, or to order a sign directly from our team, please call us today at 1-718-252-7575  or fill out our contact form for more information.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','Window Wraps | Storefront Window Graphics for Commercial Properties','','','Window Graphics Signs,Window signage,Window Signs nyc,Window Decals,Custom Window Decals'),(60,1,'Canvas printing','&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Banners Expo is, at its core, a printing company. And for many, one of the best types of prints to make is a custom canvas printing. Canvas is a material with an incredible texture, and one that can bring nearly any type of image or design to life.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    If you are in need of custom canvas printing services, call Banners Expo today. Though based in Brooklyn in NYC, we have clients around the United States, as far as California, Florida, Texas, and more. Give us a call today at PHONE NUMBER to find out more about our canvas printing services.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Who Uses Canvas Prints?&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Canvas printing is common in numerous industries, and one of the few types of prints used by both businesses and individuals alike.  There are many different uses for canvas printing, including:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Photo to Canvas Print – If you are a photographer or artist, you may need canvas printing to create your work. We have bulk rates available for those printing numerous copies, as well as the ability to provide one-time prints – all with fast shipping available.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Retail Canvas Prints – Many home décor companies create canvas prints at a large scale with different designs, phrases, quotes, and art. We work with many retail companies in NYC and abroad, designing and creating custom canvas prints for sale in stores.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;\r\n        Sign Creation – Canvas signs may not be as common, but they are a beautiful and effective way to decorate a property and share a message. Canvas signs may be used for menus, advertising, and other announcements, and created to look like an art piece or modeled after other effective forms of advertisements.\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    You’ll see canvases for sale or displayed all around New York City, included hotels, restaurants, retail stores, and homes both large and small. Our canvases have been displayed in Manhattan, Brooklyn, The Bronx, Staten Island, Queens – and as far away as Los Angeles, San Jose, Orlando, Miami, and so much more. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Our Custom Canvas Printing Options&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    From photo to canvas printing to affordable sign development, Banners Expo has a variety of options available to make sure that your canvas print is designed exactly as you envisioned. If you choose to print your custom canvas with Banners Expo, you’ll be able to choose from a variety of options including:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Sizes – We can create a custom canvas print in a variety of sizes, with a recommendation of 24 x 36 inches to ensure the canvas looks its best.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Wrapping – We offer many different types of canvas wraps as well, including gallery wrap (1.5 inches), standard wrap (.75 inches), and framing wrap (2 inches).&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Finishing – We offer lamination finishing for those that need it, increasing the lifespan of your canvas and ensuring that it continues to look its best.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Edging – We are one of the few canvas printing services that also has edging options available to help you with your print. We have both round and straight edging options available. &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We are also happy to talk to you about your specific needs. For example, if you expect the canvas to be in an area with a lot of moisture, we can talk to you about the materials that work best for you.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Send Us Your Photo/Image or Contact Us Today&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We accept images in a variety of different formats, including EPS, .AI, .PSD, .JPG, .PNG and .PDF. But what makes us a special choice for your needs is that we also have graphic designers with expertise in signs and canvas prints that can help you create a design that matches your vision. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We believe in making sure that you have the perfect design to match whatever your needs may be, and we’ll make every effort to ensure that your final design is exactly as you envisioned. For more information about our canvas printing services, or to order your own custom canvas print, please call us today at 1-718-252-7575  or fill out our form for more information.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We have a complete team of printing experts that can assist you with any part of the canvas printing process, and we’ll do our best to offer the high end customer service that you expect for your business. Contact us today to get started. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','Canvas Printing | Photo to Custom Canvas Wall Art','','','Canvas printing, Photo to canvas print,Custom Canvas printing,Canvas Printing Services'),(61,1,'Backdrops','&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Backdrops are large signs that are primarily used for photos. Also known as step and repeat banners, backdrops are a very common way to turn any event into a more memorable one, allowing others nearby to take photos and get exposure to a company’s brand. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    But backdrops have many uses, even beyond event branding. At Banners Expo, we create high quality custom backdrops that specifically designed to meet your needs. Contact us today at 1-718-252-7575 to get started. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Why Use Backdrops for Branding?&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We live in an increasingly visual world, where people can share their experiences at the click of a button. Backdrops have always had a place at events and other venues, but they have become even more important in recent years now that social media has made sharing these images and videos easier than ever before.   \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Every time someone shares a photo in front of a backdrop, you receive exposure to your brand and message that will help you with your marketing efforts. Yet it is not just for branding either. Backdrops are also great for creating memories – such as weddings, corporate events, and more. Years into the future, those that took photos in front of these backdrops will remember when they were taken fondly. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    It is for these reasons and more that backdrops are considered incredibly common in areas like:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt; Galas and Movie Releases – Backdrops are perhaps best known for their use at movie releases, in players, for award events, and other galas. Celebrities frequently take photos in front of backdrops in order to brand the event and show magazines and news where they are. &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Weddings – Backdrops are also regularly used at weddings as a way to help people remember the event and give an “official” place for people to pose for photos. &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Clubs and Music Events – Backdrops are also extremely common outside of clubs or music and comedy venues. They are popularly designed with logos and event names so that they can be shared on social media and brand the venue widely.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Backdrops are also not limited to words and logos. You can also order full color backdrops. These backdrops may be used in photography, providing a background to your photos that make it a great choice for those taking pictures. Backdrops for photography are another one of our many services that we are happy to offer all of our backdrop printing customers. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Backdrops may also be used for decorative purposes. You can put backdrops on walls to decorate a trade show or a walkway, and give an area more personality than ever before. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    At Banners Expo, our goal is to make sure that you have access to high quality backdrops in the styles and colors that you need. We are based in Brooklyn in New York City, but service not just NYC, but also Los Angeles, Atlanta, Miami – and anywhere else that requires a custom backdrop.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Our team of sign designers can create step and repeat banners that are certain to match your needs, with customization options that include:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Hemming (for Mesh Banners)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Pole Pockets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Multicolor Grommets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Custom Sizes&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Banner Stands (or No Stands)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Varying Thicknesses&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Waterproofing and UV Resistant Material&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We accept backdrop designs in multiple formats, and we can provide recommendations for those that are unsure how to create these designs effectively. We are also one of the few backdrop sign companies that can has thoroughly trained graphic designers on staff with decades of experience in backdrop design. If you have a vision for your sign and need help moving forward with its completion, Banners Expo is ready to help.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Contact Banners Expo Today to Get Started&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Based in New York and serving all of the United States, we can create backdrops in all of the colors and styles that you’ve come to expect from a quality backdrop design. With fast turnaround options available and numerous customization options, we’re confident that once you try us for your backdrop, you’ll continue to use our services for years to come.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;For more information about our sign services, or to get started on your custom sign, please call us today at 1-718-252-7575  or fill out our form, and one of our trained sign specialists will get back to you as quickly as possible. We know how important a high quality step and repeat banner is for your business, and we are ready to turn your vision into a reality. &lt;/p&gt;','','Backdrops Banner | Event &amp; Wedding Backdrops Printing','','','Backdrops Banner nyc,Background Banners,Backdrops Printing,Step and Repeat banner,Backdrops for Photography,High resolution printing Backdrops,Award ceremonies Banners'),(62,1,'Window decals','&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Window decals are an incredibly popular type of sign. More and more business owners have realized that their windows represent unused space that can easily be a great place to put your logo, your services, your products, and more. More and more companies are also using window decals as a promotional item – especially sports teams – and window decals can also go be placed on cars to turn a vehicle into a rolling advertisement.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    But not all window decals are created equal. At Banners Expo, we are experts at creating custom, affordable window decals with many bulk pricing options and customization choices that make us a great choice for your company’s needs.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;About Our Window Decal Services&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Banners Expo is a national sign company that has over 30 years of experience creating window decals, window wraps, and many other types of signage. We also create custom wall decals, and have a full range of services that are designed to match your needs. Some of our customization options include:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Lamination and Finish – We have both matte and gloss lamination available, to both protect the decal and to give it the unique look you’re going for.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Cut – We also have many cutting options for these wall decal stickers. We can create square decals, which may be easier to mount. Or we can do die cut decals that provide your decals with the ideal custom shape.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Single/Double Sided – Decals can also be made single and double sided, so that you can see images both inside and outside of the window. &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Size – One of the reasons that so many people choose Banners Expo is because we are also able to provide window decals of a variety of sizes, from small decals to full window wraps.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    We have a variety of window decal styles as well, including etched glass decals that give the appearance of carving into your window, car window decals, window lettering, frosted window decals, and so much more. If you can envision it, we can create it, and we’re sure that you’ll have the perfect decal or sign to match the appearance you were trying to achieve.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Why Custom Window Decals from Banners Expo?&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Based in NYC and serving areas as far as Los Angeles, Miami, Austin, and more, Banners Expo has become the number one choice for the development of custom window decals for both retail stores and cars. We also are one of the only national sign companies that has trained window decal graphic artists on staff to create any design that you’re looking for. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n  At Banners Expo, our experience allows us to be the ultimate choice for your window sign and window decal needs, and with so many different options to choose from, we’re confident that we are the best choice for your window sign decal development.  \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Customer Service With Decades of Experience&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Banners Expo is committed to customer service, and is there to assist you every step of the way. We have years of experience crafting decals in all different shapes and styles, working with those that are looking to increase brand exposure or decorate their storefront, and making sure that they end up with the perfect window decals for their professional needs. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Contact Banners Expo Today to Get Started&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Banners Expo is a full service sign company, capable of developing the window signs that you’ve been looking for. Our window decals are just one of our many sign related services, so be sure and ask about our full window wraps, wall decals, floor decals, and all of our affordable sign services.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n    Please call us today at 1-718-252-7575  to find out more about our window decal services, or fill out the form on the site for us to get started with your design. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','Window Decals | Frosted Vinyl and Gold Leaf Window Lettering','','','Etched Glass Decals,Clear window Decals,Window Lettering,Car window Decals,Frosted Window Decals,Window Decals,Custom Window Decals'),(97,1,'Tantex 29x69','&lt;h2&gt;Tantex 29&quot; X 69&quot; &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt; #3 grommets in corners &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt; Single sided &lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;  Basic carry bag included &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;90 day warranty against all manufacturer defects &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Variable height and expanding floor base &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','Tantex 29x69','','',''),(99,1,'Zork 37x70','&lt;h2&gt;Zork 37&quot; X 70&quot; &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;#3 grommets in corners &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt; Single or double sided &lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li&gt;  Basic carry bag included &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;90 day warranty against all manufacturer defects &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Double Sided Depth: 19&quot;  &lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','Zork 37x70','','',''),(77,1,'Gator Board','&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;Gator Board &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Out of all the foam boards available in the market, the most strongest one is the Gator Board which cannot be crushed, bended, dented and is quite sturdy and durable for travel. Not only is it the toughest but is also the most versatile printing material that you will get in the sign market.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gator board has an extra layer of covering that makes it more durable and strengthens it and makes it sturdier than a regular sign, poster or a foam board. Gator board gives you the flexibility to hang present your art work, advertisement, display or your business presentation, using the gator boards you can present you work with out without framing. Gator boards can be used everywhere, from a normal bedroom to a classy and stylish living area. Selecting the perfect image for the gator board would really bring a spark to your room.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Despite the rugged qualities of a gator board, the print and the coating of the art work ensure the quality and the color stability, with that, your image, art work, business presentation or any kind of advertisement will keep looking exactly how it did when you chose to hang it in the first place. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the use of gator boards, you would bring life to anything you are displaying on a gator board. The gator board is made up of a very light polystyrene material. Gator board is the perfect solution for retail signage, which could be either temporary or permanent, sign displays, business presentations and advertisements. With the gator board sign displayed inside your work place will increase the value and bring a certain charm to it. The gator board sign is sturdy and strong enough for reusing. These signs are printed with a vibrant and bright UV ink, making it striking and gorgeous. It is very reasonably priced and is very cost effective.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gator boards can be easily hung on walls with the use of screws, nails or any other adhesive material that would be able to hold it in place. You could even use a rope, some strings or other such material to hang your gator board from the ceiling. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The gator boards are made for the indoor use only. You should avoid placing a gator board in the area where it would be in exposure to excessive moisture. The sign should be cleaned using a dry cloth, refrain from using any liquid for cleaning the gator board sign. Take care while transporting the sign as the edges could be dented easily.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We, Banners expo are a Brooklyn based sign manufacturing company, working in Manhattan, Staten Island, Bronx and Queens. We have an entire team who would be able to meet all of your needs and requirements and even design the entire sign for you in a very striking and professional way. We would make your business our priority and not let you down.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We guarantee you completely amazing work, a cooperative management and products at a very cost effective and reasonable rate. If you have any queries regarding any of our products, feel free to contact us and we will get back to you as soon as we can.&lt;/p&gt;','','Gator Board','','',''),(50,1,'Vinyl Banner','&lt;p&gt;Banners are one of the simplest and most effective ways to draw attention. Banner signs – especially vinyl banner signs – allow you to advertise our announce a great deal of information in a way that is noticeable to anyone that walks by, and anyone that is within eye range.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;At Banners Expo, we create custom vinyl banners that are certain to make an immediate impact. With excellent quality craftsmanship, long lasting material, and the ability to customize the work to your specific needs, Banners Expo is the best choice for vinyl banner designs in New York, and the rest of the United States.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Custom Vinyl Banner Printing from Banners Expo&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nVinyl banners are useful for both indoor and outdoor use, but solid vinyl (as opposed to mesh vinyl) is an excellent choice for displaying inside of a store or building. Vinyl is extremely long lasting, capable of being moved with ease, and very easy to clean – all of which make it one of the most common and most popular choices among those looking for quality signage.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nAt Banners Expo, we can print custom banners that match the specific needs of you and your business with a variety of customization options to choose from, including:\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Seam and Seamless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Multiple Color Grommets (White, Silver, Black)\r\n    &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hemming (for Mesh Vinyl)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Pole Pocket (for Mesh Vinyl)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;13oz, 15oz, and 8oz Vinyl&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Gloss and Matte Finishing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Reinforced Webbing and Reinforced Hemming&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nWe can work with any design that you and your team send over. But one of the things that make us an even better choice for those that are in need of a banner is that we also have our own designers on staff that can help turn the vision of your vinyl banner into a reality. It is often difficult to create a design that accounts for the dimensions of the banner, the colors that look best on the material, and more. But the vinyl banner designs that we make are certain to represent the message the way you want it to appear.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Local and National Sign Development at Banners Expo&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Based in New York, Banners Expo provides banner services for both the local NYC community, as well as those that are doing business nationally. We have numerous customers in areas like New Jersey, Pennsylvania, and Massachusetts. We even have clients as far away as Florida and California.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;One of the ways that we’re able to do this is that we do our best to offer outstanding customer service and support, great rates, numerous banner options, and fast shipping and turnaround for those that need it. We have become the one stop source for all types of banner needs, including:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;Single Side Vinyl Banners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Indoor and Outdoor Ready Vinyl Banners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Billboard Vinyl Banners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Full Color Vinyl Banners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Seamless Vinyl Banners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Mesh Vinyl Banners&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nThere is essentially no limit to the vinyl banners that we can and cannot create, with dimensions that can be as much as 12 feet by 160 feet depending on the needs of you and your business. We’re also affordable enough for families and small contractors, so that those that need a custom banner sign need only ask us to create one and we’ll make it as soon as possible.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Call Banners Expo Today&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nWe know you have your choice in banner designers, banner printers, and banner services. We also know that that there are many companies both local and abroad that seem like great sign companies. But we at Banners Expo truly believe that we are the perfect choice for your banner sign needs, offering the highest quality banners with the best quality service at the most affordable prices.\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The best way to learn about our vinyl banner services is to call us today at 1-718-252-7575. We are happy to answer any questions you may have, talk to you about our dimensions and printing ability, put you in touch with our designers or speak with you about the plans you have for your design. We accept almost every design file type, including .EPS, .AI, .PSD, .JPG, .PNG &amp;amp; .PDF., and if we have any issues with quality or sizing, we’ll help you figure out what it will take to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nWhether you’re in NYC with us, or you need us to ship nationally, please contact us as soon as possible to get started. \r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','Custom Vinyl Banners Online, Order a Vinyl Banners Free Shipping Over $199 for Indoor &amp; Outdoor Advertising','','','Vinyl Banners, Custom Vinyl Banner, Vinyl Banners Printing, Single Side Vinyl Banner, Billboard Vinyl Banners, Vinyl Signs, Rush Orders Welcome, Vinyl Rush Banners'),(101,1,'Spire 26x78 ','&lt;h2&gt;Spire 26&quot; X 78&quot; &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Variable height = 59&quot; or 78&quot; &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Easy to assemble  &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Carry bag included  &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;90 day hardware warranty against manufacturer defects  &lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','Spire 26x78 ','','',''),(89,1,'Golistic 33x79 ','&lt;h2&gt;\r\n\r\nGolistic 33 X 79 &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;3-piece bungee poles &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Snap top graphic rail &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Silver base with black end caps &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Swivel feet for extra stability &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Includes carry bag &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Standard height of 78.5&quot; &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Quick and easy to assemble &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;90 day warranty against all manufacturer defects &lt;/li&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n','','Golistic 33x79 ','','',''),(55,1,'Aclima 60x83','&lt;h2&gt;Aclima 60 X 83 &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Comes complete with base, toolless quickrail, hybrid bungee/ telescoping pole and carry bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Variable graphic height: 60&quot;- 83.25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Chrome finish endcaps&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Weighted base for stability&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Adjustable leveling feet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Protective foam padding in bag&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;