insert  into `oc_review`(`review_id`,`product_id`,`customer_id`,`author`,`text`,`rating`,`status`,`date_added`,`date_modified`) values (1,0,0,'Harrison.j','Super professional, super quick turn around. I\'ve worked with a bunch of different companies who provide similar services and they are by far the best.',4,0,'2017-01-03 00:00:00','2017-03-04 03:11:56'),(2,0,0,'Patrick','Super professional, super quick turn around. I\'ve worked with a bunch of different companies who provide similar services and they are by far the best.',4,0,'2017-01-03 00:00:00','2017-03-04 03:12:04'),(3,0,0,'Jhon','Super professional, super quick turn around. I\'ve worked with a bunch of different companies who provide similar services and they are by far the best.',5,0,'2017-01-03 00:00:00','2017-03-04 03:12:18'),(4,0,0,'Williams','Great management team that allows one to work and collaborate as one sees fit. Staff had some very tenured employees so there was always a wealth of experience to draw from.',5,0,'2017-01-03 00:00:00','2017-03-04 03:12:26'),(5,0,0,' Adams','Working at Banner was great. Working with different patients and learning different things on a regular basis. Was always busy and everyone was great working as a team. Everyone was always asking if we needed anything. ',4,0,'2017-01-03 00:00:00','2017-03-04 03:12:34'),(6,0,0,' Parker','I was trusted and enabled to greatly improve the environment of care in all aspects to include safety and security for psych patients, infrastructure including wall finishes, electrical and backup power, lighting, furniture, flooring, doors and hardware, windows, plumbing, landscaping, and recreation. I worked contracted and worked with many vendors.',5,0,'2017-01-03 00:00:00','2017-03-04 03:12:40'),(7,50,0,'Jhon','I needed five roll up banners for my business expo in limited time. When I see through variety of pop up banners I ordered aclima23*83 and Briny 35*83 choose between polyester and vinyl printing with much lesser time but quality was as I expected in my mind. My trade show went good it happened with the help of team work that is only provided in sign depot.',4,1,'2017-02-07 18:57:05','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(8,50,0,'Patrick','Very fast response for my display stand and deliver what I asked for. they cropped the edges of my banner stand to fix it accord with my need and delivered my banner stand timely.',5,1,'2017-02-03 18:57:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(9,62,0,'Debby Smith','I recently started a cupcake shop and didn’t have enough funds to decorate the interior as well as the window. A friend suggested decals. I got a design for the window and some smaller identical ones for the walls. It looks perfect.',5,1,'2017-01-12 18:55:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(10,62,0,'Sam - Campaign Strategist','Signs just didn’t seem to be enough and people tend to look sideways not upwards was looking up for stuff online when I found Banners Expo and the window decals, contacted them and got the most amazing designed decal for my window that has been increasing the sales quite a lot.',5,1,'2016-11-22 19:01:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(11,56,0,'petter','Product was as described ! I was very pleased with it and it looks so beautiful on my wall.',4,1,'2016-08-18 19:02:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(12,56,0,'Bella Ross','I didn’t expect to have the exact decals for my walls as it looks in the design but its surprisingly amazing. My sitting room is looking too cool with it.',5,1,'2016-12-05 19:03:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(13,56,0,'Robert Fernandez – Entrepreneur','Wall decals are pretty amazing when worked the right way. I was a bit concerned about the rates at which I was getting the decals. I looked up a few companies and found Banners Expo that gave me the exact same thing at much cheaper costs.',4,1,'2017-02-11 19:05:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(14,57,0,'Selma Johnson','I had glass windows all around my shop and it had not been looking nice. A customer gave me the suggestion to have the names of the brands that I sold to be on the empty glass space.  I contacted Banners Expo and got the window wraps. It made the shop look much much more attractive and welcoming',4,1,'2016-11-15 19:07:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(15,57,0,'Greg, Staten Island New York','My boutique had glass windows, I had thought that it would look nice but it did not. A read about window wraps and got some made for my store. The company was very cooperative and got my wraps made quick and cheap.',5,1,'2016-11-15 19:07:50','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(16,57,0,'Reynaldo Perez','I bought a new show room and needed the window wraps like I had on all my other show rooms. I was being charged more by all the companies that I had contacted. I came across banners expo and got the job done much quicker and at cheaper rates',5,1,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(17,51,0,'Veronica','I had a stadium and needed funding. I got a suggestion to advertise some brands and be paid  for it. I contacted a company and got a few mesh banners made. They were highly appreciated and served their purpose. Banners expo did a great job.',5,1,'2016-10-10 19:09:48','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(18,51,0,'Karen and Kate','I had to have a campaign to create awareness about a certain illlness and didn’t really know how to get the advertising done. I looked it up online and found about mesh banners of banners expo. They helped me a lot in attracting people.',5,1,'2016-11-22 19:10:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(19,51,0,'Chelsea, Long Island','Thanks for Making our Company Event a Success: Planning for our first company event is nerve-wrecking, and I was tasked to make sure that the banner would be loud enough to attract attention. I don’t think I would be able to pull it off if not for Banners Expo. Imagine my relief when the boss told me, ‘Good job!’ I can’t thank you enough for such an amazing work.',5,1,'2016-11-16 19:11:11','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(20,61,0,'Jack, Brooklyn','Back drops are a must when it comes to dramatic performances, I needed backdrops and couldn’t find them anywhere, I came across Banners Expo and had a talk with them regarding what I wanted. Thanks to them, I got my backdrop made overnight and at amazingly low cost.',5,1,'2016-12-15 15:31:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(21,61,0,'Reno, New Jersey','I needed a back drop for my campaign and didn’t have much money left to spend. I found Banners expo and found out that they could do the work I wanted in the best and cheapest costs.',4,1,'2016-08-17 15:32:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(22,61,0,'Dave, Manhattan','Being a drama teacher, I needed to have backdrops at hand, coincidently, I needed one that I did not have and it was a little bit too late for that. I came across Banners expo and they made me the backdrop over night. It was the best experience ever',5,1,'2016-06-16 15:33:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(23,50,0,'Aubrey, Long Island)','Had to organize a charity event and didn’t know how to make people aware of it. Did some research and found about the vinyl banners. They are easily put up and reusable. It was a good way of promoting my event. It was very effective and attracted a large number of people',4,1,'2016-11-16 15:35:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(24,50,0,'Geena and David, Edison NJ','I had to make people aware about the DIY things I made myself. It was going to be a pain having to paint so many posters, so I did it the easy way and ordered a few vinyl banners. I just provided the company with my design, they added a bit to the design and I had my banners made overnight, at pretty amazing rates',5,1,'2016-08-30 15:37:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(25,50,0,'Denise, Staten Island','I was to work at a booth at a school fair. For luring people, I got a vinyl banner made. It was easy and cheap to get it; the company even got it made in just a single day. It attracted so many people and increased the sales. It was totally worth it',4,1,'2016-09-23 15:38:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(26,53,0,'Karen, Elizabeth NJ','I was to sell my house but couldn’t get people to have a look at it; a friend gave me the suggestion to put up a yard sign. I looked up companies and contacted a few. Banners expo gave me the quickest response, understood what I wanted them to do and I had my for sale sign ready in just 24 hours. It worked wonders.',5,1,'2016-10-26 15:39:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(27,53,0,'Timothy)','I work a hairstyling salon from home and wanted to attract those who lived nearby. I wanted to put up a yard sign that would be well designed and be able to attract people. Banners expo made me the best possible yard sign. It bought me business more than it was worth. It was an incredible experience working with Banners Expo.',5,1,'2016-12-27 15:39:35','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(28,53,0,'Cathy H','I was to have a yard sale and wanted to make people look forward to it. They wouldn’t take it seriously if I had a few hand written signs up. So I contacted Banners Expo and got a yard sign made. They even delivered it overnight and that is as fast as it gets. It was an amazing experience working with these people and incredible were the results that the sign bought.',5,1,'2017-01-12 15:40:08','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(29,59,0,'Bert C','Amazingly designed and worked well with what I wanted. As I needed them in just 24 hours, it amazed me that I actually got them.',5,1,'2016-07-05 15:41:28','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(30,59,0,'Jimmy','The management was very helpful and cooperative. They got me just what I needed. ',5,1,'2016-04-05 15:42:13','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(31,59,0,'Caroline','Got everything that I asked for in such a short time. Greatly pleased with their quality of work. Would definitely suggest them to a friend.',4,1,'2017-01-21 15:42:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(32,60,0,'Dave, store owner','Needed a few canvases made with my family pictures. Very happy with how they have turned out. Would definitely be ordering more from them and will recommend them to friends and family.',5,1,'2016-11-11 15:46:27','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(33,60,0,'Richard Smith','Quick, responsive and helpful service. They delivered the canvases I wanted in such a short time, without lessening the quality.',5,1,'2016-12-12 15:47:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(34,60,0,'Sam Taylor','I ordered a few canvases with my family pictures on them. I really wanted the quality of those to be good and they turned out to be better than I anticipated. Everyone that sees the canvases loves them. Banners expo did a great job.',4,1,'2016-09-04 15:47:53','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(35,58,0,'mike Slough','Its first time I’ve order for a magnetic sign for my vehicle and found Banners Expo easy too use and received the exact quality what I order for. Highly recommended',5,1,'2016-04-13 15:48:35','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(36,58,0,'Moris Meno','I’m running a security guard company and need vehicle sign for branding purpose. I just sent my art work to them and they deliver the sign at same day. I’m impressed how beautifully they deal with the rush orders.',4,1,'2017-02-20 15:49:10','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(37,58,0,'Roger Moi','My big truck magnet signs come great! Will use your services again.',4,1,'2016-03-17 15:49:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(38,63,0,'David H','Bought window cling signs for new business, was pleased with the quality and fast delivery.',4,1,'2016-06-27 15:51:13','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(39,63,0,'Mesika','Received my clings exactly as ordered. I was a little surprised by the excellent print quality because I\'ve had small issues in the past. Great resolution and good quality material. Easy to install and 1/3 the price of other quotes I received. Can\'t wait to order more!!!',5,1,'2016-11-29 16:34:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(40,63,0,'Boy','Windshield static cling stickers for Melo Car Workshop for its identification.',4,1,'2016-10-10 16:34:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(41,79,0,'Jimmy','I order a coroplast sign to display in stand for brand awareness Banners Expo did great job and deliver in same day with beautiful quality of printing. Job done nicely.',4,1,'2016-08-01 17:18:46','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(42,79,0,'Mahira','Our coroplast signs turned out great! Tahir was very responsive and turned our signs around very quickly. We’ll be ordering more signs in the future. Thanks team!',5,1,'2016-06-08 17:19:40','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(43,54,0,'H.Albert','Friendly customer service! Great response turn around from the time I submitted the order. I was super impressed and have already recommended your company to a friend!',5,1,'2016-11-02 17:20:42','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(44,54,0,'Mark J','We were extremely happy with the pricing and the quality of the product. We would definitely work with you in the future.',5,1,'2016-08-03 17:23:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(45,56,2,'vishali np','Product was as described ! I was very pleased with it and it looks so beautiful on my wall',4,0,'2017-02-28 23:24:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(46,0,0,'Shelley','I’m glad I made the right decision when I chose Banners Expo to install vinyl window graphics in my store. Offers Higher durability and works great!',4,1,'2017-02-15 00:00:00','2017-03-04 05:54:37'),(47,0,0,'Amber','I do event planning and styling as a profession. I have worked with Banners Expo throughout my career because I loved their commitment and ability to meet the deadlines. The backdrops that they provide me are able to add more flair to every event and party that I organize. I highly recommend them.',5,1,'2016-11-28 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(48,0,0,'Cathy H.','These guys understand exactly what we want. They offer excellent service and were very hands-on from initial survey on site, installation, removal and disposal of our banners and signs.',5,1,'2016-09-11 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(49,0,0,'Jane ','\r\nWhat can I say? You guys are terrific! I had my parents’ wedding photo done in canvas as an anniversary gift to them. It was awesome! I can’t quite put into words how their faces lit up when I gave them my gift.',4,1,'2016-08-30 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),(50,7